This paper presents a fast gradient method for support vector machines (SVMs) that can optimize various SVM models. The paper discusses the efficiency and effectiveness of the proposed method in various practical applications in artificial intelligence, such as classification and event recognition. Therefore, the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories for this paper are cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition), cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms), and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
